    <li>Preferred MVC Template - ASP.NET MVC 5</li>
    <li>Additional Plugins used: Bootstrap, Toastr, JQuery DataTables, Bootswatch Themes, Resharper</li>
    <li>Source Control: Github. Project Link: <a href="https://github.com/randalx2/ISManagement" target="_blank">Github Cloud Repo</a></li>
